OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FIt looks like the cuts to ITV's daytime
OL,6,Fschedule will mean changes to the time
OL,7,Fof the ITV Lunchtime News.
OL,9,FLorraine and Loose Women end their
OL,10,Fcurrent runs on Friday. They will
OL,11,Freturn later in the year.
OL,13,FLorraine's slot at 9.30am is being
OL,14,Ffilled by an extension to Good Morning
OL,15,FBritain.
OL,17,FHowever Loose Women is not being
OL,18,Fdirectly replaced.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,153,140,200,120,0,100
