OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FOn Monday 9th March, the ITV Lunchtime
OL,6,FNews is at 12.30pm. This is followed at
OL,7,F1pm by a repeat of Celebrity
OL,8,FCatchphrase.
OL,10,FThe afternoon schedule for the rest of
OL,11,Fthe week is devoted to the Cheltenham
OL,12,FFestival with the news earlier than
OL,13,Fusual.
OL,15,FHowever the schedule for the following
OL,16,Fweek shows the news at 12.30pm each day
OL,17,Ffollowed by more episodes of Celebrity
OL,18,FCatchphrase.
OL,20,FOf course, the change also means the
OL,21,Fregional bulletins will be brought
OL,22,Fforward by an hour to 12.55pm.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
