OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe change in the news schedule is a
OL,6,Fwelcome development from my point of
OL,7,Fview.
OL,9,FA bulletin starting at 1.30pm was too
OL,10,Flate for people on their lunch break.
OL,12,FIt seemed the news was playing second
OL,13,Ffiddle to what may have been best for
OL,14,FITV's daytime schedule overall.
OL,16,F12.30pm is a better time surely?
OL,18,FHowever the BBC News at One absolutely
OL,19,Fdominates lunchtime viewing with around
OL,20,F2m viewers. It often outrates its ITV
OL,21,Frival by three to one.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
FL,153,140,200,120,0,100
