OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G4/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FIt is unclear if the ITV News will stay
OL,6,Fat 12.30pm permanently or return to
OL,7,F1.30pm when Loose Women is back on the
OL,8,Fair.
OL,10,FHowever there seems to be a sense in
OL,11,Fthe TV world that the cuts to both
OL,12,FLorraine and Loose Women mean the shows
OL,13,Fcould now be on borrowed time.
OL,15,FThe ITV Lunchtime News has been at
OL,16,F1.30pm for around 20 years. But it had
OL,17,Fmoved around the schedule previously.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
