OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FThe programme is descended from First
OL,6,FReport ` the first full lunchtime news
OL,7,Fprogramme on British TV. It began in
OL,8,F1972 and was shown at 12.40pm. In 1974
OL,9,Fit moved to 1pm and was later renamed
OL,10,FNews at One.
OL,12,FThe programme moved briefly to 12.30pm
OL,13,Fin 1987 when ITV introduced a full
OL,14,Fmorning schedule. But this was
OL,15,Finitially unsuccessful so it returned
OL,16,Fto 1pm a few months later.
OL,18,FIn 1991, the 12.30pm slot was given
OL,19,Fanother go. The move coincided with
OL,20,Fwhat is now known as the First Gulf
OL,21,FWar.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
OL,24,ANext PageBClean FeedCNat TVFOn This Day
