OL,1,W~+$ hw1~{4~k4 ~shw1~sj7}         G6/6
OL,2,W+.!+,"-$/*%/*% / "-$+,*-'U(,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,3,GOPINIONCITV Lunchtime News on the move
OL,4,
OL,5,FIt should be remembered that the recent
OL,6,Fcuts to ITV's daytime schedule have
OL,7,Fbeen primarily driven by economic
OL,8,Fnecessity. Many people have left their
OL,9,Fjobs.
OL,11,FIf an extended GMB and an afternoon
OL,12,Frepeat of an old gameshow is more cost
OL,13,Feffective, I can envisage this becoming
OL,14,Fpermanent.
OL,16,FBut moving the Lunchtime News to a
OL,17,Fbetter slot has positives.
OL,23,EPub: 05-Mar-2026Upppppppppppppppppppppp
